GASTON COUNTY: Crowders Mountain State Park
Linwood Access. Backside Trail. Off the trail behind
erosion fence. Elev. 381 m. On slope covered in leaf
debris. Co-occurring species include Kalmia latifolia,
Sassafras spp., Smilax spp., Acer spp., and Vaccinium
spp. No flowers. Mostly new leaves.

Research and Collecting Permit, 2021_0524.
